parameters.functionCode:
const now = $now.toFormat("yyyy-MM-dd")
const leads = $('Airtable5').first().json
const jsonData = $item(0).$node['Get data1'].json;

const answersText = jsonData.answersText
  .replace(/Magic Link: .*(\n|$)/g, '')
  .replace(/Started: .*\n/g, '')
  .replace(/GA4 Session ID: .*\n/g, '')
  .replace(/GA4 Client ID: .*\n/g, '')

const duplicateAnswersText = `När registrerat: ${now} \n${answersText}`

return [{
  Email: leads.Email,
  'Duplicate Lead Answers': leads['Duplicate Lead Answers'] ? `${leads['Duplicate Lead Answers']}\n---------------------\n\n${duplicateAnswersText}` : duplicateAnswersText,
  'Duplicate Lead Count': leads['Duplicate Lead Count'] + 1
}]

  .replace(/RudderStack Session Id: .*(\n|$)/g, '')

const duplicateAnswersText = `När registrerat: ${now} \n${answersText}`

return [{
  Email: leads.Email,
  'Duplicate Lead Answers': leads['Duplicate Lead Answers'] ? `${leads['Duplicate Lead Answers']}\n---------------------\n\n${duplicateAnswersText}` : duplicateAnswersText,
  'Duplicate Lead Count': leads['Duplicate Lead Count'] + 1
}]
